is to just rehearse over and over.

124
00:08:10,089 --> 00:08:13,226
So these ten days are going to
be very important.

125
00:08:13,292 --> 00:08:17,730
Everyone's trying extra hard,
since we're entering our tenth year.

126
00:08:21,501 --> 00:08:25,371
<i>This is their second time
